  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>Ideal as a taste of this beautiful country for those wishing to explore independently. Starting in <a data-udi="umb://document/d517b2c21fa94eb096a3bcb6b7e933c5" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/bergen" title="Bergen">Bergen</a> with its famous harbour and UNESCO Bryggen Wharf, you’ll have time to explore this vibrant city known as the ‘Gateway of the Fjords’ and with its museums and reputation as a culinary centre, before transferring by scenic express boat to the serene fjordside village of <a data-udi="umb://document/a09d8dda0d4f48d68be229cdaeb2f377" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/balestrand" title="Balestrand">Balestrand</a> on the Sognefjord. Here you can enjoy a memorable day trip to Flåm and the famous rack railway to Myrdal, explore deeper into the Sognefjord or visit the impressive arms of the Jøestedal glacier before returning to Bergen for your flight home.</span></p>
<p> </p>
<div>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/taste-of-norway#Tour highlights">Tour highlights</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/taste-of-norway#Itinerary">Itinerary</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/taste-of-norway#Your holiday includes">Your holiday includes</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/taste-of-norway#Hotels">Hotels </a>| <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/taste-of-norway#Departure dates">Departure dates</a></h2>
